rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all amusement park ride accidents. These are the incidents in which something goes wrong during an amusement park ride, resulting in death or injuries and damage to the ride. These are usually on a smaller scale that mso:event.disasters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Ride Accident

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the date on which the amusement park accident occurred.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.accident to the number of deaths caused by the accident.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Deaths

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.accident to the number of people injured in the accident.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Injuries

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.accident to themso:amusement_parks.ride on which the accident occurred.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ride

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the themed subdivisions of amusement parks. For example, 'Adventureland' and 'Frontierland' are areas of Disneyland Park, and 'Medieval Faire' and 'White Water Canyon' are areas of Canada's Wonderland.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Park Area

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a subdivision of an amusement park to the amusement park itself.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Parks

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all amusement park rides that are part of Disney theme parks.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Disney Ride

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Virtual property relating an mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride to the mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride_ticket_membership relationship that contains data about the types of tickets and their eligible rides.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ticket

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type representing the collection of all Disney ride tickets. Types of tickets were issued for rides when Disney charged both an admission and tickets for rides. Currently, there is only an admission to the park. However, rides are still referred to as 'E-ticket' or 'C-ticket' to distinguish ride popularity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Disney Ride Ticket

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Relationship type collecting the data for all Disney rides and the type of ticket needed for the ride during the given time period.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Disney Ride Ticket Membership

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride_ticket_membership relationship to the start date the given ride was available to ride with the given ticket.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: From

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride_ticket_membership relationship to the mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride available for the given ticket during the time duration.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ride

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride_ticket_membership relationship to the mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride_ticket that allows a visitor to ride the given rides within the given dates.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ticket

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.disney_ride_ticket_membership relationship to the end date the given ride was available to ride with the given ticket.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: To

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all amusement parks. These are the parks commercially operated that are for fun, and usually include activities and rides.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Park

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.park to the number of visitors the park had.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Annual Visits

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.park to its identifier in the roller coaster database.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Roller Coaster Database ID

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A virtual property that relates an amusement park to a ride that is part of the park.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ride

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all amusement park rides. These are the mechanical devices that are ridden for amusement and fun.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Ride

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the mso:amusement_parks.amusement_park_area in which the ride is located.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Theme Area

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its capacity of riders per hour.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Capacity (riders per hour)

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its cost at a given date.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Cost

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the mso:amusement_parks.ride_designer(s) responsible for designing the ride.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Designer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the largest height the ride drops its riders.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Drop

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the duration of the ride in seconds.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Duration

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the minimum height a rider must be to ride.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Height Restriction

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the film.film that is presented during the ride.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Includes Film

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the number of times the riders are inverted.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Inversions

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its mso:amusement_parks.manufacturer, the company that put together the ride.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Manufacturer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its maximum g-force, which is the measurement of acceleration felt as weight.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: G-force

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its maximum speed.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Max Speed

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to the mso:amusement_parks.park in which it is located.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Park

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its mso:amusement_parks.ride_type.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Ride Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.ride to its mso:amusement_parks.ride_theme, the general subject of the ride.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Theme

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all amusement ride designers. These are the agents responsible for the conception and design of amusement park rides. This term includes the individual people, as well as departments or companies.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Ride Designer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all amusement park manufacturers. These are the companies that take the design and plans for rides and manufacture the ride.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Ride Manufacturer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type representing the collection of all amusement ride types. These are the groupings of rides that share common characteristics.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amusement Ride Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: An amusement park ride that consists of a railroad track with abrupt turns and steep slopes, on which people ride in fast trains.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Roller Coaster

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.roller_coaster to the mso:amusement_parks.roller_coaster_propulsion_system the roller coaster uses.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Propulsion

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.roller_coaster to its ID in the Roller Coaster Database ID.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Roller Coaster DataBase ID

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.roller_coaster to the length of its track.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Track Length

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:amusement_parks.roller_coaster to its mso:amusement_parks.roller_coaster_train_configuration, which is the means by which the cars are configured together.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Train Configuration

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type representing the collection of all propulsion systems used in mso:amusement_parks.roller_coasters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Roller Coaster Propulsion System

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type representing the collection of all train configurations used to attach cars to the mso:amusement_parks.roller_coast.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Roller Coaster Train Configuration
